  "detailed_description": "In the Winterland wheere everyone is in a deep winter slumber, an early summer has arrived.<br>Can Elis, the only one awake, save the Winterland?<br><br>\"Elis in the Winterland\" is an action-defense game where utilizes Elis' magics and the power of her Winterland's friends to fend off the summer heat.<br><br>As a player, you contol Elis to summon defensive friends<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/723dde5b4ba6817905998601d27c7f88.avif?t=1694197104\" width=284 height=258 /></span><br><br>and if necessary, you can use Elis' skills to defeat the enemies directly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/74da49dc7e0376f4ec383041bbef53e6.avif?t=1694197104\" width=354 height=348 /></span><br><br>Combine the defensive friends and Elis' skills strategically to withstand the invasion of the Summer Kingdom.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/40bbbc95e4d64c9f1e7b1d3a09255927.avif?t=1694197104\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>If you endure the summer invasion until the end of the summer heat, you will achieve victory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/96977757659de372866a48591d3a619a.avif?t=1694197104\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>Endure it, for when winter is coming after summer departs.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "In the Winterland wheere everyone is in a deep winter slumber, an early summer has arrived.<br>Can Elis, the only one awake, save the Winterland?<br><br>\"Elis in the Winterland\" is an action-defense game where utilizes Elis' magics and the power of her Winterland's friends to fend off the summer heat.<br><br>As a player, you contol Elis to summon defensive friends<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/723dde5b4ba6817905998601d27c7f88.avif?t=1694197104\" width=284 height=258 /></span><br><br>and if necessary, you can use Elis' skills to defeat the enemies directly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/74da49dc7e0376f4ec383041bbef53e6.avif?t=1694197104\" width=354 height=348 /></span><br><br>Combine the defensive friends and Elis' skills strategically to withstand the invasion of the Summer Kingdom.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/40bbbc95e4d64c9f1e7b1d3a09255927.avif?t=1694197104\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>If you endure the summer invasion until the end of the summer heat, you will achieve victory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365300/extras/96977757659de372866a48591d3a619a.avif?t=1694197104\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>Endure it, for when winter is coming after summer departs.</strong>",
